\c 18
\s Ukuzalwa kukaIsaka kuyathenjiswa
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala kuye \w ema-okhini\w**\x + 13.18.\x* eMamre, wathi ehlezi emnyango wethente ekutshiseni kosuku,
\v 2 wasephakamisa amehlo akhe wabona, khangela-ke amadoda amathathu\x + Heb. 13.2. Gen. 18.22; 19.1; 31.11,13; 48.16. Eks. 3.2,14; 6.3; 14.19; 13.21; 24.10. Isa. 63.9. Mal. 3.1.\x* emi phambi kwakhe; esewabonile wagijima ukuwahlangabeza\x + 19.1.\x* esuka emnyango wethente, wakhothamela emhlabathini,
\v 3 wasesithi: Nkosi, uba-ke ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, ngicela ungadluli usuke encekwini yakho.
\v 4 Ake kulethwe amanzi amalutshwana\x + 19.2; 24.32; 43.24.\x*, beseligeza inyawo zenu, liphumule ngaphansi kwesihlahla.
\v 5 Ngizaletha-ke ucezu lwesinkwa\x + Hlu. 6.18; 13.15.\x*, beseliqinisa inhliziyo yenu, beselisedlula, ngoba yikho ledlule encekwini yenu\x + 19.8; 33.10.\x*. Asesithi: Ngokunjalo yenza njengokutsho kwakho.
\v 6 UAbrahama wasephangisa esiya ethenteni kuSara, wasesithi: Phangisa! \w Amaseya\w** amathathu empuphu ecolekileyo! Xova, wenze amaqebelengwana.
\v 7 UAbrahama wasegijimela enkomeni, wathatha ithole elibuthakathaka njalo elihle, wa\add li\add*nika ijaha; laphangisa ukulilungisa.
\v 8 Wasethatha amasi lochago, lethole abelilungisile, wakubeka phambi kwawo; wema eduze lawo ngaphansi kwesihlahla, asesidla.
\p
\v 9 Asesithi kuye: Ungaphi uSara umkakho? Wasesithi: Khangela, ethenteni\x + 24.67.\x*.
\v 10 Yasisithi: Isibili ngizabuya kuwe nga\add lesi\add*sikhathi sempilo\x + 18.14.\x*; khangela, uSara umkakho u\add zakuba\add* lendodana\x + 17.19,21; 21.2. Roma 9.9.\x*. USara wa\add ku\add*zwa esemnyango wethente elalingemva kwayo.
\v 11 UAbrahama loSara basebebadala sebelensuku ezinengi\x + 17.17. Roma 4.19. Heb. 11.11,12,19.\x*; kwasekuphelile kuSara okwendlela yabafazi\x + 31.35.\x*.
\v 12 USara wasehlekela ngaphakathi\x + 17.17. Luka 1.18.\x*, esithi: Sengigugile, ngingaba lenjabulo, lenkosi yami\x + 1 Pet. 3.6.\x* isindala yini?
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuAbrahama: Kungani uSara ehleka, esithi: Isibili lami ngizazala mina sengimdala yini?
\v 14 Kukhona into enzima kakhulu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Jer. 32.17. Zek. 8.6. Mat. 19.26. Luka 1.37.\x* yini? Ngesikhathi esimisiweyo ngizabuya kuwe\x + 17.21; 18.10. 2 Kho. 4.16.\x*, nga\add lesi\add*sikhathi sempilo, njalo uSara u\add zakuba\add* lendodana.
\v 15 USara wasephika\x + Levi 19.11.\x* esithi: Kangihlekanga, ngoba wayesesaba. Kodwa wathi: Hatshi, ngoba uhlekile.
\s UAbrahama ukhulekela iSodoma
\p
\v 16 Amadoda asesukuma esuka lapho akhangela phansi eSodoma; uAbrahama wasehamba lawo ewaphelekezela\x + Roma 15.24. 3 Joha. 6.\x*.
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Mina ngingamfihlela uAbrahama yini engikwenzayo\x + Hlab. 25.14. Amos 3.7. Joha. 15.15.\x*?
\v 18 Ngoba isibili uAbrahama uzakuba yisizwe esikhulu esilamandla; lazo zonke izizwe zomhlaba zizabusiswa kuye\x + 12.3; 22.18; 26.4. Seb. 3.25. Gal. 3.8.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba ngimazile, ukuze alaye abantwana bakhe\x + Dute. 4.9,10; 6.7. Efe. 6.4.\x* lendlu yakhe\x + 17.27. Josh. 24.15.\x* emva kwakhe, besebegcina indlela yeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuze benze ukulunga lokwahlulela, ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* imehlisele uAbrahama lokho ekutshoyo ngaye.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Ngoba isikhalo seSodoma leGomora sikhulu\x + 4.10; 19.13. Jak. 5.4.\x*, langoba isono sabo sinzima kakhulu,
\v 21 ngizakwehla-ke\x + 11.5. Eks. 3.8.\x* besengibona ukuthi njengokwesikhalo sayo esesifike kimi, benzile ngokupheleleyo; kodwa uba kunge\add njalo\add* ngizakwazi\x + Dute. 8.2; 13.3.\x*.
\v 22 Amadoda esefulathele lapho, asesiya eSodoma\x + 19.1.\x*; kodwa uAbrahama wayelokhu emile phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 18.1.\x*.
\p
\v 23 UAbrahama wasesondela\x + Heb. 10.22.\x*, wathi: Kambe uzambhubhisa lolungileyo kanye lomubi\x + 20.4. Nani 16.22. 2 Sam. 24.17.\x*?
\v 24 Mhlawumbe kukhona abalungileyo abangamatshumi amahlanu phakathi komuzi; kambe uzabhubhisa ungaxoleli indawo ngenxa yabalungileyo abangamatshumi amahlanu abakuwo?
\v 25 Kakube khatshana lawe ukwenza into enjalo, ukubulala olungileyo kanye lomubi lokuthi olungileyo abe njengomubi\x + Jobe 8.20.\x*; kakube khatshana lawe; umahluleli womhlaba wonke kayikwenza ukulunga yini\x + Jobe 8.3. Roma 3.6.\x*?
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Uba ngithola eSodoma abalungileyo abangamatshumi amahlanu phakathi komuzi\x + Jer. 5.1. Hez. 22.30.\x*, ngizaxolela yonke indawo ngenxa yabo.
\v 27 UAbrahama wasephendula\x + Luka 18.1.\x* wathi: Khangela-ke, ngizimisele ukukhuluma eNkosini, lanxa ngiluthuli lomlotha\x + 2.7; 3.19. Jobe 4.19.\x*.
\v 28 Mhlawumbe kuzasweleka abahlanu kubo abalungileyo abangamatshumi amahlanu; uzabhubhisa umuzi wonke ngenxa yabahlanu yini? Yasisithi: Kangiyiku\add wu\add*bhubhisa uba ngithola khona abangamatshumi amane lanhlanu.
\v 29 Waseqhubeka elokhu ekhuluma kuyo wathi: Mhlawumbe kuzatholwa khona abangamatshumi amane. Yasisithi: Kangiyiku\add kw\add*enza ngenxa yabangamatshumi amane.
\v 30 Wasesithi: Ngicela iNkosi ingathukutheli lapho ngikhuluma. Mhlawumbe kuzatholwa khona abangamatshumi amathathu. Yasisithi: Kangiyiku\add kw\add*enza uba ngithola khona abangamatshumi amathathu.
\v 31 Wasesithi: Khangela-ke, ngizimisele ukukhuluma eNkosini; mhlawumbe kuzatholwa khona abangamatshumi amabili. Yasisithi: Kangiyiku\add wu\add*bhubhisa ngenxa yabangamatshumi amabili.
\v 32 Wasesithi: Ngicela iNkosi ingathukutheli\x + Hlu. 6.39.\x*, ngizakhuluma khathesi kuphela; mhlawumbe kuzatholwa khona abalitshumi. Yasisithi: Kangiyiku\add wu\add*bhubhisa ngenxa yabalitshumi.
\v 33 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasihamba isiqedile ukukhuluma kuAbrahama; uAbrahama wasebuyela endaweni yakhe.